info.description:
ITKBoneMorphometry provides bone analysis filters that compute features from N-dimensional images that represent the internal architecture of bone.
Please refer to:Vimort J., McCormick M., Paniagua B.,“Computing Bone Morphometric Feature Maps from 3-Dimensional Images”, Insight Journal, January-December 2017, https://hdl.handle.net/10380/3588.
info.name: itk-bonemorphometry
info.summary: An ITK module to compute bone morphometry features and feature maps
